["instr(',' ||
 (select owner
 from (select owner
 from jgcrm.os_historystep

 and action_id = 33
 and entry_id = (select instid
 from ecif.lcIB_HHSXHCLC
 where id = {0})
 order by finish_date asc)
 where rownum = 1) || ',',
 ',' || id || ',') > 0 or instr(',' ||
 (select owner
 from (select owner
 from jgcrm.os_historystep
 where step_id = 32
 and action_id <0
 and entry_id = (select instid
 from ecif.lcIB_HHSXHCLC
 where id = {0})
 order by finish_date asc)
 where rownum = 1) || ',',
